<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='27773' id='t-27773'>And you start thinking about
what you would do with this time.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='31034' id='t-31034'>And you say, &quot;I'm going to spend 
